= Entropy Power Inequalities 

== Brief Overview 


Study of entropy power inequalities with the emphasis on finding condition for the equality and stability.



== Conference 
 - A. Dytso, R. Bustin, H. V. Poor, S. Shamai (Shitz), “On the Equality Condition for the I-MMSE Proof of the Entropy Power Inequality,” 55th Annual Allerton Conference on in Communication, Control, and Computing (Allerton), Monticello, USA, October 2017.